 my career on a lot of it. I learned when I was on recruiting duty

00:00:08.060 --> 00:00:11.670
 because you're basically meeting people for the first time and having

00:00:11.670 --> 00:00:15.280
 to convince them that join the Navy is in their best interest.

00:00:15.280 --> 00:00:18.880
 It's an intangible product, and you're essentially selling it to them.

