 you know, being ableto listen and you listen well and kind of ask probing

00:00:33.310 --> 00:00:36.920
 questions to get behind that need or get behind. You know what

00:00:36.920 --> 00:00:40.520
 that surface value is because there's always something underlying there.

00:00:40.520 --> 00:00:44.130
 That's something you want to try and get to. The only way you

